Invocation Name: mystic eight
des:
A fun game to ask questions and get your fortunes told

To start, just say "Alexa, ask Mystic Eight and shake" and a question of your choice.

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
